Properties.Name: Get Parent Project GUID via SQL

Properties.Value:
SELECT Guid
FROM _com_blueboxmoon_ProjectManagement_Project
WHERE Id = (SELECT EntityId AS ProjectGUID
FROM AttributeValue
WHERE AttributeId = '16217' AND Value = '{{ Workflow | Attribute:'ReservationId' }}')
